{"tid":1862752,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我想問呢兩千位醫護是否陰鳩肯罷嘅七千位醫護？","createTime":"2020-02-04T20:02:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T03:21:35.000Z","uid":167548,"like":30,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"150e5e61e03146311d9a914f56ababcfece5b26b","tid":1862752,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T20:02:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3GqiuKC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3GqiuKC.jpg&h=3d34316a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我無罷工 我有野想講你聽<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1862480\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1862480</a><br />\n可以去呢個Post睇下咩叫賤人就是嬌情.....<br />\n<br />\n利申在此再向肯罷抱有敬意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你地贏左其他工會成員會出嚟攞尾彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 我真是好費解 「gay罷工大台」出Post話比工會醫護好想落台是點？見好就收？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇嗰勢星期五完結就真罷工結束<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 社區爆發醫護返翻崗位, 真自求多福啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nHa從來唔當你地是人咁洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CNgQ5ks.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCNgQ5ks.jpg&h=b8c4bcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有自稱醫生回覆話外人唔好比意見, 全部FreeRider<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真是好耶, 班仆街左膠唔見佢地對勇武行動出少句聲, 坐監唔是你坐, 人地拎條命去搏㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n假如醫護到最尾返翻去崗位, 聽中共發落, 聽天由命, 被中共道德綁架<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 祝你好運啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申深夜放負, 恨鐵不成鋼<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6c40104aff6f82f22c0d89234194aac7fc0e5a","tid":1862752,"uid":167548,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T20:06:21.000Z","msg":"每次香港人輸在堅持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不如比7000位罷工手足自己投票決定返唔返崗位啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1b6dbdc2cf3a250a50b9d4733931bebf9043f47","tid":1862752,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T20:08:42.000Z","msg":"同意請正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf0183cada3aa76acd71bd9bcf80f3e0e24e04f8","tid":1862752,"uid":295572,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T20:09:00.000Z","msg":"唔係唔封關、唔復工咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6100b430a4386f53f7c00d5552f6ae73965eec1","tid":1862752,"uid":133763,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T20:09:10.000Z","msg":"上帝搵到位比果兩千位醫護<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d554a932b4452b5c0bd9fac7342f0847aaba83b5","tid":1862752,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T20:09:27.000Z","msg":"負評當同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa55f64ae0bc17ac4157a3cefc05ad9f7462d05","tid":1862752,"uid":147182,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T20:09:38.000Z","msg":"仲話唔會怪罷工個啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肯出黎罷工個啲就俾人擺晒上枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"033015b6f00bfc9d795a800837d959779de76a58","tid":1862752,"uid":