2,"uid":167548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8d43471b1027cb4597981083a965f63a91a6a918","tid":1862752,"uid":56205,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf0183cada3aa76acd71bd9bcf80f3e0e24e04f8","tid":1862752,"uid":295572,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T20:09:00.000Z","msg":"唔係唔封關、唔復工咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T20:24:59.000Z","msg":"社區爆發咗 封關黎做乜？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T20:32:23.000Z","msg":"依家仲未到社區爆發<br />\n最多叫做本地人傳人<br />\n全面封關依然有用<br />\n沙士個陣淘大花園先叫社區爆發"},{"pid":"6b278e42fcf4eafeeaec45d4d0e258d5bef081fd","tid":1862752,"uid":295572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d43471b1027cb4597981083a965f63a91a6a918","tid":1862752,"uid":56205,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf0183cada3aa76acd71bd9bcf80f3e0e24e04f8","tid":1862752,"uid":295572,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T20:09:00.000Z","msg":"唔係唔封關、唔復工咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T20:24:59.000Z","msg":"社區爆發咗 封關黎做乜？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T20:35:46.000Z","msg":"想社區唔爆發十日前就應罷工，<br />\n社區爆發係預咗，<br />\n但醫護罷工也是勢在必行嘅事，<br />\n咁叫價就一定係封關，<br />\n逼令到政府封關有好大嘅意義，<br />\n逼唔到亦有其他得著...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d149ce6e8c9457ea8cee2c085041336ceb1ecd","tid":1862752,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d43471b1027cb4597981083a965f63a91a6a918","tid":1862752,"uid":56205,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf0183cada3aa76acd71bd9bcf80f3e0e24e04f8","tid":1862752,"uid":295572,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T20:09:00.000Z","msg":"唔係唔封關、唔復工咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T20:24:59.000Z","msg":"社區爆發咗 封關黎做乜？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T20:36:20.000Z","msg":"講封關無用論 Biggest argument 是 支那人驚左病毒唔落嚟播毒 and 被人搞大左再中出都無所謂啦........."},{"pid":"3cea53e57c8cd67acfdd8592051ddfd606609749","tid":1862752,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T20:36:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"98d407bafb62a09e8451e40df39d7dd054af3cf6","tid":1862752,"uid":295572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c0fcfb908419aa51987bea872e9682577927b62","tid":1862752,"uid":96708,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T20:14:45.000Z","msg":"如果有病人因為全部人罷工而病死你咪又賴嗰兩千個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T20:43:34.000Z","msg":"唔會，佢哋有八萬醫護大軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（醫管局人手總計有79,659人。）"},{"pid":"eff0bb4a2c55235bb3b87dd640a6e074c24fc8f1","tid":1862752,"uid":19178,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4c0fcfb908419aa51987bea872e9682577927b62","tid":1862752,"uid":96708,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T20:14:45.000Z","msg":"如果有病人因為全部人罷工而病死你咪又賴嗰兩千個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T20:59:27.000Z","msg":"唔明點解會賴嗰兩千個<br />\n全部人肯罷 咁個兩千個就唔會單獨抽出嚟講啦<br />\n而且仲有個垃圾正苦係到 要賴都係賴佢啦(正苦根本應該要take曬所有責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n仲要未講仲有班盲撐政府 叫9罷工嘅醫護辭職 藍絲醫護坐陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我想問<br />\n如果好多人好似個兩千個人咁諗 (話支持 最後玩嘢嘅)<br />\n結果得好少人罷 哩批有風骨嘅醫護比人清算<br />\n佢地怪邊個?<br />\n<br />\n我真係屌曬你班陰鳩人嘅醫護<br />\n其實你唔罷 咪沉默 靜靜雞囉 唔好投票囉 唔好講咩支持啦<br />\n你支持你自己咋 <br />\n唔好同我講咩 有班病人要睇住(你估罷工個班唔想同你地掉轉?)<br />\n點解作為當時人支持罷工 自己唔罷工 但要求更多人罷工<br />\n(支持示威者 但唔好阻到佢日常生活 希望示威者加油 咁樣?)<br />\n<br />\n開個post講咩<br />\n&quot;要令到更多人加入/被加入罷工團隊<br />\n如果今次我哋唔撐過去<br />\n當權者只會更加得寸進尺&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我想講其實佢咁做已經助長緊當權者嘅氣焰<br />\n更加唔好提 你一個所謂嘅'支持'係會令工會同埋罷工嘅人誤判形勢<br />\n好唔好意思呀"},{"pid":"9f9ba3b0e06360cc699333d7ed7af08a47fc8aab","tid":1862752,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T22:11:12.000Z","msg":"成班傻閪成日諗住點輸點輸，後果幾撚慘 轟轟烈烈浪漫主義英雄式失敗<br />\n但唔去諗點樣贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cb60dbf55999861f50c82f05e81639356e88614","tid":1862752,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d43471b1027cb4597981083a965f63a91a6a918","tid":1862752,"uid":56205,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf0183cada3aa76acd71bd9bcf80f3e0e24e04f8","tid":1862752,"uid":295572,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T20:09:00.000Z","msg":"唔係唔封關、唔復工咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T20:24:59.000Z","msg":"社區爆發咗 封關黎做乜？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T22:12:37.000Z","msg":"封關都係其次<br />\n連PPE都冇返乜撚工呀成班黑護奴隸死賤種"},{"pid":"aa6c7f76c74862241984c67fb5695e1f366c01e0","tid":1862752,"uid":46822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T22:14:54.000Z","msg":"甚實簽左名又唔罷係點<br />\n彈出彈入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"881ee78b2506b9d6b0b195c1b3981761d2f12a22","tid":1862752,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T20:21:45.000Z","msg":"算了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 美帝快啲封埋香港關啦, 帶頭封鎖香港啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}